# Directories excluded from plugin installation.
#
# NOTE: .pluginignore is NOT a standard Claude Code feature (as of March 2026).
# No AI coding tool (Claude Code, Copilot, Cursor, OpenCode) supports build
# phases or install-time file exclusion. This file serves as:
#   1. Documentation of intent — these dirs are NOT part of the runtime plugin
#   2. A convention we'd like to see adopted as a standard
#   3. Input for a future build.sh if needed
#
# If you're building a plugin installer or marketplace, please consider
# supporting this file format (one glob pattern per line, # comments).

# Build sources — fragments, templates, generators
src/

# Development files
*.test.sh
.github/
